{"tid":1877911,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"先文鬥後武鬥！律師彼此看不爽怒丟炸彈　法院爆炸多人受傷","createTime":"2020-02-13T09:36:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-13T10:47:44.000Z","uid":32511,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"10b35b943df1e931ed61c46322a1134688057b7d","tid":1877911,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T09:36:44.000Z","msg":"《新德里電視台》報導，印度北方邦（Uttar Pradesh）首府勒克瑙（Lucknow）一處法院今（13）日下午發生爆炸事件，造成至少兩名律師受傷，目擊者表示，在現場起碼發現2枚炸彈。《今日印度》指出，據了解，疑似是兩團不同的律師代表發生爭執，才會導致這起事件。<br />\n <br />\n根據《今日印度》（INDIA TODAY），勒克瑙一處法院今日傳來爆炸聲響，詳細地點位於<br />\nHazratganj，靠近當地地方法官的辦公室，其中有一人受到重傷，另外兩人則是輕傷。當地消息指出，有兩派律師團出現爭執，接著就有爆炸聲響，疑似是為了攻擊法庭上的律師所為。<br />\n <br />\n勒克瑙律師協會聯合秘書長洛迪（Sanjeev Lodhi）聲稱，自己是被攻擊的目標。警方已確認，利用炸彈進行攻擊的是亞達夫（Jeetu Yadav），疑似使用當地所製造的爆炸裝置。當局正在調查這起事件時，警方又在現場發現3枚炸彈。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9QLPf78.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9QLPf78.jpg&h=09745769&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/NewsNationTV/status/1227863031905804289\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FNewsNationTV%2Fstatus%2F1227863031905804289&d=2Od897eOL%2Byk6rGVR7zebY5RPfZ%2FgKFUZzIsJfjgB6g%3D&h=0534055c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FNewsNationTV%2Fstatus%2F1227863031905804289&h=ccc6a9ab\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/NewsNationTV/status/1227863031905804289</a>"},{"pid":"0ff3f36f634046e30cd690ca5159a3e8ad5cf68b","tid":1877911,"uid":24457,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T09:37:11.000Z","msg":"以為香港"},{"pid":"6da3526538e58f59f296bcbd39814be609acedaf","tid":1877911,"uid":32511,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T09:38:09.000Z","msg":"炸完陪審團全部跳舞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11f7